1
00:00:08,160 --> 00:00:12,080
Kuizhou honors plumpness.

2
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:16,040
A woman's full figure is highly valued.

3
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:17,400
The skinny girls

4
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:20,200
must obey the guilt order,

5
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:21,800
become the lowest class,

6
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,280
serve as slaves,

7
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:25,280
and barely survive.

8
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,240
Only a plump beauty

9
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,560
is what gentlemen desire.

10
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:30,840
Speaking of which,

11
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:34,280
the most gorgeous plump beauty in our state

12
00:00:34,360 --> 00:00:38,000
is the owner of the cosmetic shop Yanzhi Pavilion,

13
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:39,280
Fang Qingcheng.

14
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:40,640
Master Fang

15
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:42,600
is born rich, elegant,

16
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,000
and noble.

17
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:44,920
And today

18
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:47,160
is her wedding day with the Third Lord of the Governor's Mansion,

19
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:50,360
Chu Shengyi.

20
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:53,120
She is here.

21
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,880
A lord from the Governor's Mansion

22
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:59,080
is really marrying a businesswoman.

23
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:00,320
Fang Qingcheng

24
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:02,320
has made it to the top.

25
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:03,520
I am so jealous.

26
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,120
It is almost time to light up.

27
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,480
Madam.

28
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:20,480
Have mercy.

29
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:25,760
The back door is locked due to the Lord's wedding.

30
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,840
I was forced

31
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,360
to enter through the front door.

32
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:32,400
Have mercy.

33
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:33,120
Madam.

34
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,700
The bride has arrived.

35
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,680
Miss.

36
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:39,960
The time...

37
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,640
Let me go take a look.

38
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:47,250
We can't afford to offend Madam Li.

39
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:48,640
Wait a moment.

40
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:50,759
Madam.

41
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,520
Mother.

42
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,320
This

43
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,400
new skinny slave doesn't know the rules.

44
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,920
She bumped into you.

45
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,600
I will

46
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,100
help you punish her later.

47
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,440
But the auspicious time is almost over.

48
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,480
Can the bride come in first?

49
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,120
I misspoke.

50
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,040
Mother.

51
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,280
You're getting married.

52
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,840
You should be more thoughtful

53
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,600
and careful from now on.

54
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,280
I will keep your teachings in mind.

55
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,400
This can't go on.

56
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,800
Hold on, Miss.

57
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,130
Hold on a little longer.

58
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,920
Let me go check again.

59
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,600
It is too late.

60
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:06,660
This...

61
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,240
Why did it expire so fast?

62
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,600
Why is there no movement?

63
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,720
Hold on a little longer, Miss.

64
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:17,650
I will rush them.

65
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,160
Why did it expire so fast?

66
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,600
The transformation rouge my grandmother left behind

67
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,880
has run out.

68
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:47,079
I thought I'd finish the ceremony before 9 p.m.,

69
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,720
but it got delayed.

70
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,040
What should we do?

71
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,640
There is no other way.

72
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,120
To get Qionghua,

73
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,930
this is our only chance.

74
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,280
Madam Li

75
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,280
hates skinny girls.

76
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,440
If you go in like this,

77
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,520
you'll be killed.

78
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:10,680
The auspicious time has come. Welcome the bride.

79
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,560
I have to get Qionghua

80
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,490
to make the transformation rouge.

81
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:18,160
Today, Qionghua is only available in Madam Li's mansion.

82
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,200
This time, Qionghua will be used as a bridal gift.

83
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,560
She will personally bestow it.

84
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,560
It is the best opportunity to get it.

85
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,000
No matter how dangerous it is today,

86
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,600
in order to turn back into Qingcheng,

87
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,260
I must complete this wedding.

88
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,640
Get Qionghua.

89
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,140
With your current figure,

90
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:35,460
Madam Li will see through you at a glance.

91
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:38,040
I can only hide it for as long as I can.

92
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,440
Qionghua.

93
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:54,440
The bride and groom are paying their respects.

94
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:57,320
First bow to heaven and earth.

95
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,640
Young Madam, retreat three inches with your right foot.

96
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,840
One inch less is considered disrespectful.

97
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:02,960
So many rules.

98
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:07,160
Oh no, why has this cushion sunk?

99
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,600
Second bow to the parents.

100
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:13,080
When bowing, keep the fan parallel to your face.

101
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:21,200
Husband and wife bow to each other.

102
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,360
Who are you?

103
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:48,480
Isn't the owner of Yanzhi Pavilion a chubby beauty?

104
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,680
Why is she a thin girl?

105
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,840
Mother, please allow me to speak.

106
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,770
This person is not Fang Qingcheng.

107
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,320
You!

108
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,120
Who are you?

109
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,840
Where is Fang Qingcheng?

110
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,160
How dare you disturb the Third Young Master's wedding!

111
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,120
Take her down!

112
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,520
Madam,

113
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,000
I have something to say.

114
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,040
I am Fang Qingcheng's younger sister, Fang Zhuozhuo.

115
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,160
Because it concerns my cousin and the Third Young Master's lifelong happiness,

116
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,840
I risked my life to marry in her place.

117
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:15,920
Please let me finish.

118
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,480
If Madam still wants to punish me after hearing me out,

119
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,480
I only ask for an intact corpse,

120
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:24,440
so that my cousin can recognize her flesh and blood when she returns.

121
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,640
Cousin?

122
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:35,930
I thank Madam for the opportunity to explain.

123
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,960
My cousin, Fang Qingcheng,

124
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,000
was preparing for the Makeup Selection Ceremony

125
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,120
supervised by Madam in two months.

126
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,320
She worked hard every day,

127
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:46,080
swearing to present Madam with a stunning makeup look.

128
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:46,920
Yesterday,

129
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:50,760
my cousin personally went to the back mountain to collect rare flowers.

130
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,600
Until now,

131
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,159
there has been no news of her.

132
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:57,240
My cousin loves the Third Young Master deeply,

133
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:59,800
and I couldn't bear to see this good match missed.

134
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:02,460
That's why I risked my life to marry in her place.

135
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,860
I know I deserve to die a thousand deaths,

136
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:08,800
but I hope Madam and the Third Young Master can understand

137
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,360
the true sisterly affection between us.

138
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:14,640
What a deep sisterly bond.

139
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:18,200
Then I will grant your wish

140
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:21,380
and reward you with an intact corpse.

141
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,840
Madam is perceptive.

142
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:26,400
I did have selfish motives for doing this.

143
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,160
I

144
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:31,880
have actually admired the Third Young Master for a long time.

145
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:34,920
I know my status as a flower slave is low,

146
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,440
and I am truly not worthy of the Governor's Mansion.

147
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,440
But if there was even a one-in-a-ten-thousand chance,

148
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,720
I wanted to try.

149
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,720
Flower slave.

150
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:45,250
Was the Third Young Master's deceased birth mother also...

151
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:50,159
A flower slave? Interesting.

152
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,360
Yi'er.

153
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:57,600
Your father is still ill.

154
00:07:57,600 --> 00:08:00,260
Since you have established your own household,

155
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:01,760
whether to kill

156
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,200
or to marry,

157
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,760
it's up to you.

158
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,520
It is all my fault.

159
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,840
I have caused you trouble, Mother.

160
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,440
The Sin Appearance Teaching

161
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:27,120
is the physical standard Mother set for the women of Kuizhou.

162
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:30,720
If we let this skinny woman marry into the estate as a substitute,

163
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:33,809
it would truly waste Mother's painstaking efforts.

164
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,640
However,

165
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,220
this Fang Zhuozhuo

166
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,480
is Qingcheng's cousin.

167
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,880
If we just kill her,

168
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:44,840
I truly cannot bear to hurt Qingcheng.

169
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,920
How about this?

170
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,400
Qingcheng will be my primary wife.

171
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,280
As for you,

172
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,210
you can stay as a concubine.

173
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,560
Thank you, Madam.

174
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:02,080
Thank you, Third Lord.

175
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,800
Since she's not the Young Madam,

176
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,600
cancel the flower bestowal.

177
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,080
Take the Qionghua away.

178
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:23,160
What exactly is this woman intending to do?

179
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,680
I didn't get the Qionghua today,

180
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:34,560
so I can only stay here and look for another chance.

181
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,560
I must survive tonight safely first.

182
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,400
My lord.

183
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:52,960
Let me

184
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,880
help you undress.

185
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:57,840
Come.

186
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,170
Come.

187
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,680
Forgive me, my lord.

188
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,840
The wedding candle went out,

189
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,800
I'm afraid it's a bad omen.

190
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,880
For our wedding night, my lord,

191
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,680
why don't we postpone it?

192
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:24,480
You said

193
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,180
you've admired me for a long time,

194
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,930
and risked your life to marry as a substitute.

195
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,560
You aren't even afraid of death,

196
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,340
so are you afraid of a bad omen?

197
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:40,720
My lord.

198
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:45,640
I am truly sincere towards you.

199
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,800
Then I must ask,

200
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:55,000
what exactly do you admire about me?

201
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,080
I am quite curious.

202
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,480
I

203
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:04,520
once saw you from afar.

204
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:07,000
You have such elegant bearing,

205
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,600
and I could never forget it.

206
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,200
If that's the case,

207
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,320
and you have nothing else to say,

208
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,770
don't waste this beautiful night.

209
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,660
Mourning clothes?

210
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,730
Forgive me, my lord.

211
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:33,400
Someone in my family passed away last month,

212
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,800
and my mourning period isn't over.

213
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,040
I know this violates etiquette,

214
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,480
but given the emergency,

215
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,120
I hope you can show some pity,

216
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:44,080
and let me observe the mourning period with a pure body,

217
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,920
before I come to serve you.

218
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:55,800
If so,

219
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,560
I won't force you.

220
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,640
If you have any news about Qingcheng,

221
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,240
tell me immediately.

222
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:12,560
Of course.

223
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:15,960
Farewell, my lord.

224
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:29,360
My lady.

225
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,720
Nanny.

226
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:32,880
My lady,

227
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:34,480
are you alright?

228
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:35,920
My heart

229
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:37,480
was in my mouth.

230
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,400
Fortunately, you were alert.

231
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:42,280
Otherwise, today's mess would've been hard to resolve.

232
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:44,880
Thanks to the news from Wuming Workshop in the black market,

233
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,000
which let us know.

234
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,680
This Madam Li,

235
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:50,720
although she dotes on Chu Shengyi in public,

236
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:53,120
actually suppresses him at every turn.

237
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:55,050
Today is her son's wedding.

238
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:56,760
On such an auspicious day...

239
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,720
She actually killed someone.

240
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,970
I bet that she would use my status as a flower slave

241
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,580
to humiliate Chu Shengyi.

242
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,080
Now that

243
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:07,920
the Qionghua is gone,

244
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:10,340
how do we make the transformation rouge?

245
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,240
As things stand,

246
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:22,600
we can only steal it from the Chief Commander's Mansion.

247
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:25,130
Madam Li's birthday banquet is in three days.

248
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:27,040
This is a good opportunity.

249
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,500
It's too dangerous, Miss.

250
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,840
The mansion has strict rules.

251
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,080
You are a concubine,

252
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,560
so you can't attend the banquet.

253
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:36,160
If concubines enter without being summoned,

254
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,640
they will be beheaded!

255
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,720
The Qionghua is rare

256
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:41,600
and very hard to grow.

257
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:45,240
Over the years, I've read all the ancient books

258
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,970
and tried countless formulas,

259
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,480
only to find out that Qionghua

260
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:51,000
is the key to making this transformation rouge.

261
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,200
Now, looking at the entire Central Plains,

262
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:56,330
only Madam Li's private garden in Qiwu Courtyard has it.

263
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:59,000
If I don't have this transformation rouge,

264
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,400
with my looks,

265
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,280
I won't even be qualified for the preliminary selection of the Makeup Ceremony,

266
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:08,520
let alone leading Yanzhi Pavilion to win first place.

267
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:09,440
But...

268
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,610
Say no more, Granny.

269
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,080
My mind is made up.

270
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,200
The moon is full.

271
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:32,220
An old friend returns.

272
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:37,480
I've finally found someone who looks like you.

273
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,820
As long as I marry Fang Qingcheng,

274
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,240
kill her,

275
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:45,880
and let you take the position of his wife,

276
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:49,200
you won't have to suffer humiliation in Quantan anymore.

277
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,320
Wait for me a little longer.

